long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing summarize-gpt: Your Instant Web Page Summarizer

Get to the heart of any web page in seconds!

Tired of wading through endless text to find the key points?
Wish you could quickly grasp the main ideas without losing focus?

summarize-gpt is here to help you browse smarter and faster.

It uses the Google Gemini API to summarize the text content.
